Abstract: Recognizes the mottled duck as the official state waterfowl.
Proposed law designates the mottled duck as the official state waterfowl. Authorizes its use
on official documents with insignia of the state.
(Adds R.S. 49:170.26)
Summary of Amendments Adopted by House
The Committee Amendments Proposed by House Committee on Judiciary to the original
bill:
